    "A diagonal reference line is added for ease of comparison.",
    "Data points above the line indicate trials where ChatGPT outperformed humans, and those below show where humans had higher accuracy.",
    "Outliers are circled.",
    "In evaluating the alignment between ChatGPT's choices and linguists' judgements, we observed that for 133 of the 148 pairwise phenomena, ChatGPT's judgements mirrored those from the linguists.",
    "This indicates that in 133 of the 148 sets of grammatical and ungrammatical sentence pairs designed by linguists, ChatGPT accurately deemed the grammatical sentences as more acceptable than their less grammatical counterparts."
